      "id": "allegoria",
      "name": "Allegoria",
      "description": "<span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Normal Attack</span><br/>Proclaims a decree in the primordial tongue and performs up to 3 attacks that deal <span style=\"color:#FF9999FF\">Pyro DMG</span>.<br/><br/><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Charged Attack</span><br/>Consumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal <span style=\"color:#FF9999FF\">AoE Pyro DMG</span> to opponents in front of her after a short casting time.<br/><br/><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Plunging Attack</span><br/>Nicole plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Also deals <span style=\"color:#FF9999FF\">AoE Pyro DMG</span> upon impact with the ground.",
