      "id": "revelation_uncreated_light",
      "name": "Revelation: Uncreated Light",
      "description": "Recreates a fleeting glimpse of an age long past, when the angels acted on the authority of the heavens, bestowing the <b><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Grace of Kenosis</span></b><b></b> effect on nearby party members. This increases their ATK and deals <span style=\"color:#FF9999FF\">AoE Pyro DMG</span>, as well as creates a Shield of Blazing Light.<br/>The Shield of Blazing Light's DMG Absorption is based on Nicole's ATK, and it will absorb <span style=\"color:#FF9999FF\">Pyro DMG</span> at 250% effectiveness.",
